1.6
log
@Extensive rewrite of pscube.  Started from scratch and patterned after
Hale's psimage.  Faces of the cube now rendered as three separate
images, rather than as a single image.  Eliminates stretching artifacts
of previous versions.  Also added support of alternate input formats
and removed VM bottleneck previously present when entire data cube
is input.
@
text
@d511 1
@


